TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Compare Stage Claim summary info with Distrubtuion Summary. Does it match? Compare Distribution Summary with GL transaction summary. Does it match? For PostAPC and Outcomes, comare GL transaction summary with PMT transaction summary. Does it match? If any does not match, set Balanced to FALSE. Added, if no PMT info for Distribution, set PMT to zeros.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_Balance_Summaries

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(isnull(SMRY_INV_AMT_PMT_in) , 0 , SMRY_INV_AMT_PMT_in )
--if no info for DSTR, set this summary to zero.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: SMRY_INV_AMT_PMT_var

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(isnull(SMRY_ADJ_AMT_PMT_in) , 0 , SMRY_ADJ_AMT_PMT_in )
--if no info for DSTR, set this summary to zero.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: SMRY_ADJ_AMT_PMT_var

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(isnull(SMRY_PAY_AMT_PMT_in) , 0 , SMRY_PAY_AMT_PMT_in )
--if no info for DSTR, set this summary to zero.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: SMRY_PAY_AMT_PMT_var

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF($PMWorkflowName = 'wf_m_CASH_Balance_StageClm_GL' , TRUE --This balance not needed, hardcode TRUE , IIF(SMRY_ADJ_AMT_STG = SMRY_ADJ_AMT_DS AND SMRY_PAY_AMT_STG = SMRY_PAY_AMT_DS , TRUE --balanced , FALSE --NOT balanced ) )
--Don't do this balance when only Dstribustion Summary and GL compared. ---- [this occurs during PreAPC and APC runs]
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: STG_DS_Balanced

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(SMRY_INV_AMT_STG + SMRY_ADJ_AMT_STG = SMRY_INV_AMT_GL + SMRY_ADJ_AMT_GL AND SMRY_PAY_AMT_STG = SMRY_PAY_AMT_GL , TRUE --balanced , FALSE --NOT balanced )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: STG_GL_Balanced

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF($PMWorkflowName = 'wf_m_CASH_Balance_StageClm_GL' , TRUE --This balance not needed, hardcode TRUE , IIF(SMRY_INV_AMT_STG+SMRY_ADJ_AMT_STG = SMRY_INV_AMT_PMT_var+SMRY_ADJ_AMT_PMT_var AND SMRY_PAY_AMT_STG = SMRY_PAY_AMT_PMT_var , TRUE --balanced , FALSE --NOT balanced ) )
--Don't do this balance when only Dstribustion Summary and GL compared. ---- [this occurs during PreAPC and APC runs]
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: STG_PMT_Balanced

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(STG_DS_Balanced AND STG_GL_Balanced AND STG_PMT_Balanced , TRUE --all balanced , FALSE --NOT balanced )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: Balanced

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Summarize Staged Claims for Distributions in 15=Transmissing status, total Adjustments and Payments.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_Smry_StageClms

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select s.DSTR_GID as DSTR_GID , sum(s.ADMN_PEND_INV_AMT+s.BASE_PEND_INV_AMT+s.PERF_PEND_INV_AMT +s.FRMLY_PEND_INV_AMT+s.CTRC_PEND_INV_AMT+s.PRC_PTCT_PEND_INV_AMT) as SMRY_INV_AMT , sum(s.ADMN_PEND_ADJ_AMT+s.BASE_PEND_ADJ_AMT+s.PERF_PEND_ADJ_AMT +s.FRMLY_PEND_ADJ_AMT+s.CTRC_PEND_ADJ_AMT+s.PRC_PTCT_PEND_ADJ_AMT) as SMRY_ADJ_AMT , sum(s.ADMN_PEND_DSTR_AMT+s.BASE_PEND_DSTR_AMT+s.PERF_PEND_DSTR_AMT +s.FRMLY_PEND_DSTR_AMT+s.CTRC_PEND_DSTR_AMT+s.PRC_PTCT_PEND_DSTR_AMT) as SMRY_PAY_AMT from vrap.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR dh , vrap.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_TXN_STG s where dh.DSTR_STAT_CD=15 and dh.DSTR_GID=s.DSTR_GID group by s.DSTR_GID order by s.DSTR_GID

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Full Outer Join summaries from Staged Claims/Distribution Summary/GL transactions with PMT transactions
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_STG_DS_GL_PMT

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Full Outer Join summaries from Staged Claims and Distribution Summary
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_STG_DS

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Because of Full Outer Join, need to determine the DSTR_GID [could be from either source]
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_DstrGID_STG_DS

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Summarize GL [SAP] transactions for Distributions in 15=Transmissing status, total Adjustments and Payments.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_Smry_GL

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select gd.DSTR_GID as DSTR_GID , sum(case when gd.GL_DOC_TYP_CD in ('RB','RF','PB','PF') then gd.GL_POST_AMT else 0 end) as SMRY_INV_AMT , sum(case when gd.GL_DOC_TYP_CD in ('WO','BA') then gd.GL_POST_AMT else 0 end) as SMRY_ADJ_AMT , sum(case when gd.GL_DOC_TYP_CD in ('RT') and substr(gd.GL_POST_ACCT_ID,1,1)='5' then gd.GL_POST_AMT else 0 end) as SMRY_PAY_AMT from vrap.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR dh , vrap.RCNT_RECN_GL_DSTR_DTL gd where dh.DSTR_STAT_CD=15 and dh.DSTR_GID=gd.DSTR_GID group by gd.DSTR_GID order by gd.DSTR_GID

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Because of Full Outer Join, need to determine the DSTR_GID [could be from either source] Added, if no GL info for Distribution, set GL info to zero.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_DstrGID_STG_DS_GL

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(isnull(SMRY_INV_AMT_GL_in) , 0 , SMRY_INV_AMT_GL_in )
--if no info for DSTR, set this summary to zero.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: SMRY_INV_AMT_GL

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(isnull(SMRY_ADJ_AMT_GL_in) , 0 , SMRY_ADJ_AMT_GL_in )
--if no info for DSTR, set this summary to zero.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: SMRY_ADJ_AMT_GL

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
iif(isnull(SMRY_PAY_AMT_GL_in) , 0 , SMRY_PAY_AMT_GL_in )
--if no info for DSTR, set this summary to zero.
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: SMRY_PAY_AMT_GL

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Summarize Distribution Summary for Distributions in 15=Transmissing status, total Adjustments and Payments.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_Smry_DstrSmry

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select ds.DSTR_GID as DSTR_GID , 0 as SMRY_INV_AMT , sum(ds.ADMN_PEND_ADJ_AMT+ds.BASE_PEND_ADJ_AMT +ds.PERF_PEND_ADJ_AMT+ds.FRMLY_PEND_ADJ_AMT +ds.CTRC_PEND_ADJ_AMT+ds.PRC_PTCT_PEND_ADJ_AMT) as SMRY_ADJ_AMT , sum(ds.ADMN_PEND_DSTR_AMT+ds.BASE_PEND_DSTR_AMT +ds.PERF_PEND_DSTR_AMT+ds.FRMLY_PEND_DSTR_AMT +ds.CTRC_PEND_DSTR_AMT+ds.PRC_PTCT_PEND_DSTR_AMT) as SMRY_PAY_AMT from vrap.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR dh , vrap.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_SUMM ds where dh.DSTR_STAT_CD=15 and dh.DSTR_GID=ds.DSTR_GID group by ds.DSTR_GID order by ds.DSTR_GID

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Summarize PMT [RPS] transactions for Distributions in 15=Transmissing status, total Adjustments and Payments.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_Smry_PMT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select pd.DSTR_GID as DSTR_GID , 0 as SMRY_INV_AMT , sum(case when pd.TXN_TYP_CD in ('Q','M','U') then pd.ACCS_RBAT_AMT+pd.MKSR_RBAT_AMT+pd.ADMN_DISCNT_AMT else 0 end) as SMRY_ADJ_AMT , sum(case when pd.TXN_TYP_CD in ('P') then pd.ACCS_RBAT_AMT+pd.MKSR_RBAT_AMT+pd.ADMN_DISCNT_AMT else 0 end) as SMRY_PAY_AMT from vrap.RCNT_RECN_DSTR_HDR dh , vrap.RCNT_RECN_PMT_DSTR_DTL pd where dh.DSTR_STAT_CD=15 and dh.DSTR_GID=pd.DSTR_GID group by pd.DSTR_GID order by pd.DSTR_GID

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Email Subject
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: FAILURE: Transactions are OOB during Recon Transmission [%d]

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Email Text
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
%a<$PMTargetFileDir/f_Dstr_Xmit_Transaction_OOB.out> Attached is a list of Distribution Transaction(s) that are Out-of-Balance for the CASH Recon Transaction Transmission process. Balancing was performed between the Staged Transaction Claims, Distribution Summary, GL transactions and PMT transactions.
The Distribution Status has been set to [99] Error. The Transmission process will proceed with good Distributions.
ONCALL: Please investigate the reason for the Out-of-Balance. When the resaon has been determined and fixed, the Distribution will need to be re-submitted to the CASH Recon Transaction Transmission process.
The format of the attached file is: Distribution GID Staged Claims Invoice Amount Distribution Summary Invoice Amount GL Transaction Invoice Amount PMT Transaction Invoice Amount Staged Claims Adjustment Amount Distribution Summary Adjustment Amount GL Transaction Adjustment Amount PMT Transaction Adjustment Amount Staged Claims Payment Amount Distribution Summary Payment Amount GL Transaction Payment Amount PMT Transaction Payment Amount
PLEASE NOTE that for PreAPC and APC runs, that the PMT Amounts will be zero. Amounts are NOT sent to RPS during PreAPC and APC runs.
